ActFirst Nations Fiscal and Statistical Management Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Schedule to the First Nations Fiscal and Statistical Management Act
PrecisOrder Amending the SCHEDULE TO THE FIRST NATIONS FISCAL AND STATISTICAL MANAGEMENT ACT by removing one First Nation and adding ten others, in order to allow them to participate in the property tax regime established by the FIRST NATIONS FISCAL AND STATISTICAL MANAGEMENT ACT.
